        "text": "and brought him by night",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] i.e. that same night, starting off early in the night and travelling during night-time, thus getting clear away from Jerusalem before the ambush of the Jews was prepared.",
